Okuma Corporation Logo Okuma Corporation is a machine tool builder based in Ōguchi, Aichi Prefecture, Japan. It has global market share in CNC machine tools such as CNC lathes, machining centers, and turn-mill machining centers. The company also offers FA products and servomotors. It is listed on the Tokyo Stock Exchange and is a component of the Nikkei 225 stock index. Source
